name: 777 Cap - Purple
description:
This digital version of the Purple 777 Cap comes with its physical one. 
Every Skele consumer that will buy this cap physically will receive this NFT gifted to their wallet. 

The number of editions is in exact correlation with the quantity of caps that were crafted in Montpellier, France. 

Garment collection initially dropped on 11/05/2021.

www.skele.rip

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
